  "about": {
    "subtitle": "Connecting iGEM teams to share synthetic biology education resources, outreach ideas, and collaboration opportunities.",
    "paragraphs": [
      "SynEdu Global is a synthetic biology education platform jointly launched by ZJU-China, Westlake, and XJTLU-China — three iGEM teams. It is dedicated to sharing educational resources, inspiring teaching ideas, and uniting iGEMers worldwide to advance synthetic biology education.",
      "We believe iGEM education grows through openness, sharing, and collaboration, not working alone. SynEdu Global started as a small idea among three Chinese teams. Our goal is to bring together talented iGEMers to build a pure, open platform centered on inspiration and science outreach. We hope every team passionate about education can find support, spark creativity, and share the warmth of science here.",
      "We invite iGEM teams, educational nonprofits, companies, and other organizations interested in science outreach to join SynEdu Global. Your suggestions, support, projects, and ideas can help us grow. We look forward to working with you — sharing outcomes, exchanging ideas, advancing education, and connecting the world — to light the spark of synthetic biology education everywhere through collaborative effort."
    ]
  },
